VIEWTECH Srl - Italy. VIEWTECH Srl - Italy is a Industrial Automation company. Viewtech is a company that provides food package inspection solutions. VIEWTECH Srl - Italy employs 4 people (+100.0% YoY), founded in 2002. Headquartered in Reggio Emilia, Italy.
[...]
Viewtech is an Italian manufacturer of vision inspection systems for the quality control of food packaging.
[...]
Viewtech solutions verify and certify the quality of many industrial products such as:
 - food packages: sliced products trays, steak trays, flat pouches or cans;
 - seals, gaskets, technical pieces;
 - pharma packages;
[...]
Performed controls by Viewtech equipment include:
 - seal integrity;
 - printed data position and correctness: expiry date, batch code, product number;
 - barcode position and correctness;
 - label position and conformity;
 - label integrity;
 - top film and labe(s) congruity
 - product quality;

Despite being a relatively young business, Viewtech already reached a groundbreaking position in the development and application of this technology and is now relating with companies on an international level, within a highly globalised market, where the quality of products and services is now above and beyond the standards.
